{"tid":1794194,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[吹雞]德國馬格尼茨基人權法立法聯署告急（30/12 deadline)","createTime":"2019-12-23T02:49:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-26T14:57:01.000Z","uid":274996,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"944e72cc5d7c17427f1170a448e752f5a49935c8","tid":1794194,"uid":274996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T02:49:14.000Z","msg":"12月30日前要有50000個簽名，而家只有5000 個，仲爭45000. 德國係歐盟大佬，佢既取態好關鍵。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/petitionen/_2019/_10/_01/Petition_99914.nc.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fepetitionen.bundestag.de%2Fpetitionen%2F_2019%2F_10%2F_01%2FPetition_99914.nc.html&d=HJ1jiXHXfxJ2%2FxolOfbUwc4e4tfxBia5339duguOAPM%3D&h=7da1e9f4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/petitionen/_2019/_10/_01/Petition_99914.nc.html</a><br />\n<br />\n呢個人權法如果立得成，會對中共高官造成重大打擊，特別係同新疆集中營，打壓政治維權人仕，干預香港人權有關既中港官員。<br />\n<br />\n請大家唔好怕煩簽哂佢。做得幾多得幾多，仲有推其他行動post, 少少野都唔做點對得住犧牲既手足！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原post 有講詳情，仲有請推post. <br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1792855\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1792855</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B1Cypxs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB1Cypxs.jpg&h=72f9c87e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6c29d09d187f5256740de071fa6b1fcd69573016","tid":1794194,"uid":114487,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T02:49:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VgwZ4tD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVgwZ4tD.jpg&h=52b479a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TGepv8D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTGepv8D.jpg&h=265d7544&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ocgLfAm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FocgLfAm.jpg&h=e2a8e121&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7f